description.zh: 不花冤枉钱，直击喜欢的！ 1、罗罗诺亚·佐罗（88.1g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，前后路飞脸部打盒，左右配件碰撞明显，系列zui轻 关键词：明盒、zui轻 	 2、妮古·罗宾（90.6g） 手感特征：上下空间巨大（约2指半），前后在封面路飞左手处哐哐打盒，左右在图鉴山治对立面处明显打盒，整体较空 关键词：轻、上下空间大、打盒点清晰 	 3、蒙奇·D·路飞（92.5g） 手感特征：上下约1指半空间，四面打盒感强，前后在路飞额头处打盒，左右在甚平图鉴处哐哐打盒 关键词：四面灵动、打盒感均匀 	 4、奈美（97.1g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，配件打盒明显，前后在背面中下部打盒，左右在图鉴对立面处打盒，四面晃动较大 关键词：中等重量、打盒点分散 	 5、撒谎布（97.2g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，前后摇不动且路飞右手处对顶明显，左右轻微晃动，四面较满 关键词：明盒、对顶感强 	 6、弗兰奇（98.5g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，配件打盒，前后在背面中上部打盒，左右在佐罗图鉴处明显碰撞 关键词：中等重量、打盒点集中 	 7、隐藏款-五档路飞（约103g） 手感特征：整体较满，上下微晃，前后中部对顶，左右晃动空间更大，系列无底座 关键词：无底座、对顶感独特 配件：无底座（干燥剂约10g） 	 8、山智（111.6g） 手感特征：上下1指半空间，六面空间大，前后在路飞脸部打盒，左右高位打盒明显 关键词：明盒、六面灵动 	 9、甚平（114.8g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，前后封面中上部打盒明显，左右配件碰撞感强，娃体微晃 关键词：打盒点偏高、配件干扰 	 10、萨波（117.7g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，前后背面中部打盒，左右较满，中上部碰盒 关键词：重量集中、打点明确 	 11、特拉法尔加·罗（118g） 手感特征：上下几乎摇不动，配件底座打盒，左右空间大（约1指半），中部哐哐打盒 关键词：明盒、左右空间大 	 12、布鲁克（119.3g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，配件打盒明显，中部有滑动物体，左右中部微碰盒 关键词：配件干扰、滑动物体 	 13、托尼托尼·乔巴（131.2g） 手感特征：上下半指空间，四面较满，前后隐约摸到物体，断层感明显 关键词：大明盒、断层重 	 ps： 重量优先：乔巴、萨波、罗等重量级易区分，隐藏款路飞无底座是关键 打盒点：注意前后/左右打盒位置 ﻿#盲盒﻿ ﻿#泡泡玛特﻿ ﻿#五档路飞﻿ ﻿#拉布布﻿ ﻿#航海王﻿ ﻿#手感攻略﻿ ﻿#攻略﻿ ﻿#我的盲盒分享﻿ ﻿#日常拆盲盒﻿ ﻿#海贼王﻿﻿

description.zh: 隐藏 路飞（五档） 重量：100.93g 手感：上下摇整体轻微打盒，但空间很小，有干燥剂颗粒声。前后摇主体完全摇不动，干燥剂包撞盒明显。左右摇主体摇不动，干燥剂包轻微打盒。前后捏中部能捏到物体，无顶盒；左右捏明显能捏到袋子，底部能捏到物体，无顶盒。 托尼托尼·乔巴 重量：133.4g 手感：上下轻微晃动，底部打盒，四面比较满，基本摇不动。中部轻按有阻碍感。 布鲁克 重量：120.6g 手感：上下有空间，晃动在底部打盒，前后微微晃动，中部碰盒。左右比较满，中部轻按有阻碍感。 萨波 重量：120.4g 手感：整体偏满，六面基本摇不动。上下轻按中部有阻碍感，四面中部轻按有顶盒感。 甚平 重量：116.1g 手感：上下基本摇不动，只有配件上下打盒。四面比较满，前后微微晃动，中间偏下位置打盒。左右基本摇不动。 特拉法尔加·罗 重量：115.6g 手感：上下空间很大，晃动明显，底部打盒。四面摇动感觉很散，前后中部轻按有阻碍感，左右中上部分轻按有阻碍感。 山智 重量：112.5g 手感：上下有空间，晃动明显，底部打盒。四面摇动，都在偏下位置均匀打盒。 弗兰奇 重量：97.6g 手感：上下空间很大，晃动明显，底部碰盒。四面空间不大，轻微摇动在中部打盒。 撒谎布 重量：97.4g 手感：上下有空间，晃动在底部碰盒。前后轻微晃动，能感觉到配件。左右摇不动，中部轻按有阻碍感。 奈美 重量：97.1g 手感：上下晃动，底部砸盒。四面比较空，摇动都在中部偏下位置均匀打盒。 妮古·罗宾 重量：93.5g 手感：上下晃动明显，配件上下打盒。四面也很空，摇动都在中部位置均匀打盒。 罗罗诺亚·佐罗 重量：93.2g 手感：上下晃动，能感觉到配件打盒。四面都有空间，摇动都在中间偏下位置均匀打盒。 蒙奇·D·路飞 重量：90.0g 手感：上手比较轻，上下晃动，在底部碰盒。前后空间不大，左右晃动，在中部打盒。 ﻿#labubu海贼王﻿ ﻿#labubu海贼王换娃﻿ ﻿#labubu海贼王系列﻿ ﻿#labubu联名海贼王﻿ ﻿#海贼王labubu﻿ ﻿#海贼王Labubu﻿ ﻿#Labubu海贼王﻿ ﻿#labubu联名海贼王﻿ ﻿#海贼王labubu﻿ ﻿#海贼王盲盒﻿
description.en: Hide Luffy (Fifth gear) Weight: 100.93g Feeling: Swing up and down, the whole box is slightly slight, but the space is very small, and there is a sound of desiccant particles. The main body cannot shake completely, and the desiccant pack will hit the box obviously. Shake the main body left and right and cannot shake it, and gently turn the desiccant pack into the box. The middle part of the front and back can pinch the object, without a top box; the left and right pinch can obviously pinch the bag, and the bottom can pinch the object, without a top box. Tony Tony Chopper Weight: 133.4g Feeling: Slightly shaking up and down, boxed at the bottom, full on all sides, basically unable to shake. A light press in the middle makes a sense of obstruction. Brooke Weight: 120.6g Feeling: There is room for up and down, shaking at the bottom, swaying slightly from front and back, touching the box in the middle. The left and right are relatively full, and the middle is lightly pressed to make it feel obstructed. Sabo Weight: 120.4g Feeling: Overall full, basically unable to shake on the six sides. Press the upper and lower middle part to feel blocked, and press the upper box to feel. Jinping Weight: 116.1g Feeling: It can’t shake up and down, only accessories can be packed up and down. The four sides are relatively full, swaying slightly in front and back, and the box is placed in the lower middle position. It can't shake left and right. Trafalgar Rowe Weight: 115.6g Feeling: Large up and down space, obvious shaking, boxed at the bottom. The shaking of all sides feels very dispersed. The light pressing of the front and back middle part will make a sense of obstruction, and the light pressing of the left and middle part will make a sense of obstruction. Shanzhi Weight: 112.5g Feeling: There is room on the top and bottom, shaking is obvious, and the bottom is boxed. Shake all sides, and evenly put the box in the lower position. Franky Weight: 97.6g Feeling: Large space for up and down, obvious shaking, and the bottom touches the box. There is not much space on all sides, so you can sway it in the middle to make a box. Lie cloth Weight: 97.4g Feel: There is room on the top and bottom, shake at the bottom and touch the box. Slightly shaken back and forth, you can feel the accessories. It can't shake left and right, and it feels obstructed when pressing the middle lightly. Nami Weight: 97.1g Feel: Sway up and down, smash the box from the bottom. The four sides are relatively empty, and the shaking is evenly shaking in the lower middle position. Nico Robin Weight: 93.5g Feeling: Swaying up and down obviously, accessories are boxed up and down. The four sides are also empty, and the box is evenly shaking in the middle. Roronoa Zorro Weight: 93.2g Feel: Sway up and down, you can feel the accessories being boxed. There is space on all sides, and the shaking is evenly placed in the lower middle position. Monkey D. Luffy Weight: 90.0g Feeling: Lighter at the beginning, shaking up and down, touching the box at the bottom. description.zh: 首先看一下隐藏盒普通款在塑料壳内的状态，都是脸朝前正放的，P2P3能看出来整个罐子是卡在中间的，和盒子四周有一定的距离，所以前后捏盒子是没有办法捏到罐子的，普通款就更捏不到了娃了。 具体区分方法有下面几点（重点3和4）： 1.重量（不靠谱），网上大部分帖子都说隐藏300+，普款只有290+，虽然轻的肯定不是隐藏，但是超过300的也有很多翻车的，非常不靠谱！！我没有称，所以不知道这盒重量。 2.干燥剂，隐藏没有干燥剂，两个普款在娃背面有大包干燥剂，但是卡在塑料壳里，声音非常非常小，几乎听不出。 ❗❗3.按压塑料壳的棱，P4隐藏塑料壳里卡的是一个硬的罐子，用两只手大拇指和手腕连接处左右按压的时候，能感受到图片中橙色的那条塑料壳的棱，‼️‼️巨硬‼️‼️用再大的力也一点按不动的，就感觉是一个硬的东西抵住了一样（放大版砖妹的棱的感觉），普款则是能感受棱，但是是软弹的，稍微用点力就嘎吱嘎吱的弹。 ❗4.在极黑的条件下，摇晃盒子，感受卡片在哪一侧，然后拿手电筒去照，能看出来卡片的影子，普款，隐藏都能看出来‼️ 所以喜欢的姐妹们千万别买那种什么标着未拆盒概率隐藏的，全骗人的！ ❤️最后提前祝大家新年快乐，新的一年都能抽到自己喜欢的娃❤️ #泡泡码特 #labubu #labunu可口可乐搪胶 #隐藏 #神秘嘉宾labubu #盲盒手感分享
description.en: First, let’s take a look at the state of the hidden box in the plastic shell. They are placed face forward. P2P3 can see that the entire jar is stuck in the middle and is at a certain distance from the box. Therefore, there is no way to pinch the jar when pinching the box front and back, and the ordinary one can’t pinch the baby even more. The specific methods of distinguishing are as follows (key 3 and 4): 1. Weight (unreliable). Most posts on the Internet say that 300+ is hidden, and the general model is only 290+. Although the lightest ones are definitely not hidden, many of them have failed over 300, which is very unreliable! ! I didn't weigh it, so I don't know the weight of the box. 2. Desiccant, hidden and without desiccant. The two common models have large bags of desiccant on the back of the baby, but they are stuck in the plastic shell, and the sound is very, very small and almost inaudible. ❗◝3. Press the edge of the plastic shell. The P4 hidden plastic shell is a hard jar. When pressing left and right with the connection between the thumbs and wrists of both hands, you can feel the edge of the orange plastic shell in the picture.‼ ️‼ ️Great hard‼ ️‼ ️No matter how strong you use, you can't press it at all, and it feels like a hard thing is pressing against it (the feeling of enlarged version of the brick girl's edge). The ordinary version can feel the edge, but it is soft and elastic, and it will creak with a little force. ❗4. Under extremely dark conditions, shake the box, feel which side of the card is, and then use the flashlight to shine it. You can see the shadow of the card. It can be seen in ordinary styles and hidden‼ ️ So sisters who like it must not buy the kind that is marked with the probability of unopening the box, it is all lie! ❤️Finally wish you a happy New Year in advance and you can draw your favorite baby in the new year❤️ #Bubble Code Special #labubu #labunuCola Cola Glue #Hide #Mysterious Guest Labubu #Blind Box Sharing

description.zh: 下班路过大悦城，进店逛一圈摇了一遍盒，台面上没什么熟悉的手感。最后路过Labubu看不见我，拿起就放不下了，这不是大神们分享的隐藏手感吗 1️⃣重量 重量93.6g，台面偏轻的盒 	 2️⃣手感 1、上下 上下大约有半指空间，我这只娃配件在上，在顶面可以感受到配件撞盒的声音 2、前后 前后上半部分大面积打盒，详见图2和图3，如果轻微摇动，会感觉到封面almost字母s处有点状打盒，拆开后发现刚好是配件发条的位置。 最重要的来了❗能明显感受到只有上半部分在剧烈晃动，下半部分完全不动，也就是大家所说的分层感。我把娃倒过来摇动，由于配件到盒子底部，所以打盒位置会非常低，差不多在二维码位置。此时顶部也没任何晃动感。 3、左右 左右也有打盒，打盒高度与前后一致，打盒面积也是一片，但我这只左右打盒感明显弱于前后。 	 3️⃣摆放位置 盒内摆放位置如图4 	 4️⃣编码 如图5 	 5️⃣干扰项 看到网上说这只手感会翻车滴滴暗号（摆放凑巧的话，也会有一半打盒一半不动的可能性），但滴滴暗号110g左右，比隐藏重15g以上，我建议可以拿台面上的超市疑云（前提得有，个人认为这个系列最明的盒，盒子底部拍手掌，会有弹簧duang duang duang的震动感）做个对比，滴滴暗号和超市疑云重量差不多。 	 最后祝大家欧气满满，抽中心愿款 #泡泡玛特 #盲盒 #labubu看不见我系列 #labubu #偷偷开心 #大人也要玩玩具
description.en: After get off work, I passed by Joy City, went into the store and swayed the box. There was no familiar touch on the counter. Finally, I passed by Labubu and couldn't see me, so I couldn't put it down. Isn't this the hidden feel shared by the masters? 1️⃣ Weight Weight 93.6g, a light box on the countertop 2️⃣ feel 1. Up and down There is about half a finger space up and down. My baby's accessories are on top, and you can feel the sound of the accessories hitting the box on the top. 2. description.zh: 寻找MOKOKO系列11款盲盒的手感和重量攻略包括隐藏款，希望能帮你提高命中率！ 1、HACIPUPU - 重量114.82g HACIPUPU手感：上下摇有两指的空间，左右摇有明显的打盒声，左边尤其明显。整体尺寸不算大。 2、小甜豆 - 重量115.4g 小甜豆手感：上下摇能明显听到干燥剂的声音，左右摇不打盒，记得斜对顶试试。 3、CRYBABY - 重量108.44g CRYBABY手感：上下摇能感觉到卡片在动，前后左右都很满，没有松动的迹象。 4、PINO JELLY - 重量114.01g PINO JELLY手感：上下只有半指的空间，底部打盒，干燥剂的声音超级大。 5、Molly - 重量113.32g Molly手感：上下也是半指的空间，左右摇盒空间有点松动，整体摇起来不是太动。 6、Mokoko - 重量106.32g Mokoko手感：上下摇晃时，有一指的空间，但不会太打盒。左右基本摇不动，只能听到卡片的声音。后面上方稍微有点打盒的感觉。 7、Dimoo - 重量135.7g Dimoo手感：这家伙挺沉的，上下摇有一指多一点的空间，前后左右基本摇不动。右侧拉布布的地方有轻微的打盒声。 8、SKULLPANDA - 重量115.32g SKULLPANDA手感：上下大概一指半的空间，底部有打盒声，左右中间也能感觉到。 9、Labubu - 重量113.32g Labubu手感：上下左右都摇不动，感觉非常满，几乎可以说是明盒了。 10、Hirono小野 - 重量121.13g Hirono小野手感：上下摇几乎不动，前后空间比较大，左右摇有打盒声，干燥剂的声音也比较大。 11、毕奇 - 重量125.51g 毕奇手感：上下感觉很满，左右摇有明显的卡片声音，前后能感觉到娃体在晃动。 ﻿#寻找mokoko﻿ ﻿#寻找mokoko系列手办﻿ ﻿#寻找mokoko系列﻿ ﻿#尋找mokoko系列盲盒﻿ ﻿#寻找MOKOKO系列﻿ ﻿#寻找mokoko系列盲盒﻿ ﻿#带上兴趣出门﻿ ﻿#先出发再说﻿ ﻿#不为打卡的旅行﻿ ﻿#时髦存档﻿﻿
description.en: Find the feel and weight of the 11 blind boxes in the MOKOKO series, including hidden models, hoping to help you improve your hit rate! 1. HACIPUPU - Weight 114.82g HACIPUPU feel: There is room for two fingers when shaking up and down, and there is a clear sound of boxing when shaking left and right, which is especially obvious on the left. The overall size is not large. 2. Little sweet beans - Weight 115.4g Little sweet beans feel: You can clearly hear the sound of desiccant when shake up and down. You can shake left and right without hitting the box. Remember to try diagonally facing the top. 3. CRYBABY - Weight 108.44g CRYBABY feel: You can feel the card moving when shake up and down, the front, back, left and right are full, and there is no sign of looseness. 4. PINO JELLY - Weight 114.01g PINO JELLY feel: There is only half a finger on the upper and lower sides, and the bottom is boxed, and the sound of the desiccant is super loud. 5. Molly - Weight 113.32g Molly feel: The upper and lower parts are also half fingers, and the left and right shaking box space is a bit loose, so the overall shaking is not too moving. 6. Mokoko - Weight 106.32g Mokoko feel: When shaking up and down, there is room for one finger, but it won't be too boxed. The left and right cannot shake, and only the sound of the card can be heard. It feels a bit like a box above the back. 7. Dimoo - Weight 135.7g Dimoo feel: This guy is quite heavy, with more than one finger to shake up and down, and basically can't shake back and forth, left and right. There is a slight sound of boxing in the labubu on the right. 8. SKULLPANDA - Weight 115.32g SKULLPANDA feel: about half a finger up and down, there is a sound of boxing at the bottom, and you can feel it in the left and right middle. 9. Labubu - Weight 113.32g Labubu feel: It can’t shake up and down, left and right, and it feels very full, and it can almost be said to be a box. 10. Hirono Ono - Weight 121.13g Hirono Ono feels: It can hardly move up and down, with a large space in front and back, with a box sound from left to right, and the sound of desiccant is also relatively loud. 11. Biqi - Weight 125.51g Biqi's feel: It feels full up and down, and there is a clear sound of card shaking left and right, and you can feel the baby's body shaking in front and back. ﻿#Find mokoko﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿

description.zh: Labubu是由香港插画家Kasing Lung于2015年创作的角色，最初出现在他的故事系列《The Monsters》中。Labubu以其尖尖的耳朵和九颗锯齿状的牙齿而闻名，展现出调皮可爱的形象。自2019年起，Kasing Lung与中国玩具公司泡泡玛特（Pop Mart）合作，推出了多种Labubu搪胶系列产品，包括盲盒、挂件等，深受收藏家和名人喜爱。 图片转自ramy#labubu
description.en: Labubu is a character created in 2015 by Hong Kong illustrator Kasing Lung, who first appeared in his story series The Monsters. Labubu is known for its pointed ears and nine jagged teeth, showing a naughty and cute image. Since 2019, Kasing Lung has cooperated with Chinese toy company Pop Mart to launch a variety of Labubu elution series products, including blind boxes, pendants, etc., which are deeply loved by collectors and celebrities. Image reproduced from ramy#labubu

description.zh: 古灵精怪的labubu动物系列终于来了~在我看来整套设计可圈可点，这次的小伙伴终于站起来了！异常可爱！（特别是小绵羊，好像老奶奶👵🏻打毛线，异常戳我的点！） 🎉 重 【🐿️松鼠】101g 全系列最重之一，区别于鲸鱼和考拉，轻捏盒子中下方摸一圈！一定会在一个面摸到一个小凸点！！记住有个小凸点！ 【🐨考拉】96g 比较重，整体分布均匀，四周摸不到东西，摇不动满盒！盒子下半部分比较重。 【🐳鲸鱼】100g 上下轻微摇晃，四周摸不到东西，前后抵住盒子，轻按封面鲸鱼的左耳朵处，有啪嗒啪嗒的声音（据说有的盒子是可以摸到对顶的！看胎位吧） 中等 【🦘袋鼠】79g 上下有摇晃空间，前后左右微微打盒，打盒在盒子居中位子。 【🐻浣熊】84.5g 整个盒子都能摇得动，干燥剂的声音很明显！卡拉卡拉的声音异常明显！有点头重脚轻！ 【🐗野猪】80g 分布比较均匀，盒子上半部分摇晃的比较厉害，下半部分微微打盒。左右打盒感明显，前后微微打盒（由于胎位放置问题，归结于一面明显打盒一面不明显！！） 【💧水母】87g 上下空间很大！摇起来下半部分打盒声音很敦实！感觉盒子上方是空的，都集中在盒子中下部分！ 【🐑绵羊】81g 左右空间大，上下空间小！在盒子上中部打盒！ 轻 【🐧企鹅】70g 全系列最轻，轻满轻满，整个娃卡的很死，摇起来只有干燥剂的声音（看胎位，有的能在盒子里面飞~） 【🦁狮子】73.2g 轻满型，上下有一点点空间，前后左右几乎没有打盒处，摇盒有干燥剂的声音，四周摸不到东西（据说狮子每个盒子都不太一样，大家随缘吧😂） 【🐵猴子】78g 上下空间小，前后左右摇不太动，左右在狮子图鉴处隐约能摸到对顶！ 【🦔刺猬】78.1g 很空很轻，上下空间非常大，摇起来感觉里面的娃很小一只，摇盒卡片撞击盒子的声音很大，干燥剂声音不明显！ #labubu #盲盒手感分享#labubu伪装动物 #labubu精灵天团伪装动物系列 #泡泡玛特 #小七潮玩铺子 #我的盲盒分享 #盲盒 #跟拉布布一起遛弯儿 #潮玩 #潮玩手办 #盲盒隐藏 #大人也要玩玩具 #盲盒 #盲盒 #潮玩手办#潮玩开箱
description.en: The quirky labubu animal series is finally here~ In my opinion, the whole design is remarkable, and this time my friends finally stood up! Extremely cute! (Especially the little lamb, it looks like an old lady 👵🏻beat yarn, and poke my dots abnormally!) 🎉 Heavy [🐿️Squirrel] 101g One of the heaviest in the whole series, different from whales and koalas, gently pinch the box and touch it in the bottom! You will definitely find a small convex point on one side! ! Remember there is a small bump! 【🐨 Koala】96g is relatively heavy, the overall distribution is even, and there is no need to touch anything around, and the box cannot be shaken! The lower part of the box is heavier. 【�Whale】100g shakes slightly up and down, and there is no thing around. Press the box forward and backward to the cover whale, and there is a clicking sound (it is said that some boxes can be touched to the top! Look at the fetal position) Medium 【🦘 Kangaroo】79g There is room for shaking up and down, and the box is slightly swaying in front, back, left and right, and the box is in the middle of the box. 【🐻 Raccoon】84.5g The whole box can be shaken, and the sound of the desiccant is very obvious! The sound of Karakara is extremely obvious! A little too heavy! 【🐗Wild Boar】80g is distributed evenly, the upper part of the box shakes violently, and the lower part is slightly boxed. The feeling of boxing on the left and right is obvious, and the front and back is slightly boxing on the front and back (due to the problem of placement of the tire, it is attributed to the obvious side of boxing on the other side not obvious!!) [💧Jellyfish] 87g has a lot of space on the upper and lower end! The sound of shaking the lower part of the box is very solid! I feel that the upper part of the box is empty, and it is concentrated in the middle and lower part of the box! 【🐑Sheep】81g has a large space around and a small space up and down! Box in the middle of the box! Light [🐧 Penguin] 70g The whole series is the lightest, light and full, the whole baby card is very dead, and there is only the sound of desiccant when shaken (just to the position of the fetus, some can fly in the box~) [🦁 Lion] 73.2g Light and full, with a little space up and down, there is almost no boxing in front, back, left and right, and there is no sound of desiccant in the box, and there is no thing around (it is said that every box of lion is different, let’s go with the flow 😂) [🐵 Monkey] 78g The space up and down is small, and it is not too moving in front, back, left and right, and you can vaguely touch the top at the lion’s picture book! 【🦔 Hedgehog】78.1g It is very empty and light, with a large space on the upper and lower ends. When you shake it, you feel that the baby inside is very small. title.en: DIMOO Disney - Hidden feel, pure Ming box! - Xiaohongshu

description.zh: ‼️重点：一组对立面，多处长条状对顶！爆顶！另一组对立面无顶。（重量，手感都不重要，找条状对顶就完了） 1⃣️前后完全摇不动，P2，P3蓝色涂鸦处明显长条状对顶，正面Dimoo字母处最明显！大拇指放上去就能感觉到。靠近下面的是前后对称顶盒的，稍微轻轻的按压一下就能感觉到。大力摇P3左上角橙色方框处能感受到一个配件在打盒。（纯看配件摆放位置了，打盒点会不一样） 2⃣️上下，左右几乎都是摇不动的，上下是因为娃高，左右是因为配件和干燥剂在两边塞住了，配件在图鉴面，干燥剂在条码面（小包干燥剂）。上下摇只能能听见干燥剂在里面晃动的声音。 3⃣️P4底部开盒摆放，本盒娃脸朝后正放的，正面Dimoo处的条状对顶是船的屁股，靠下的两条是底盘。 总体来说是非常明的盒，和Labubu可口可乐的隐藏很像，找条状对顶就行。 Dimoo开着威利号摇啊摇，太可爱了！祝大家遇到都不要错过哦。 #泡泡玛特 #dimoo新品 #DIMOO迪士尼联名 #盲盒手感分享 #盲盒隐藏 #明盒隐藏 #隐藏手感分享 #隐藏 #威利号船长 #DIMOO迪士尼系列隐藏
description.en: ‼ ️Key points: One set of opposites, multiple long strips facing each other! Top-up! Another group of opposites has no tops. (Weight and feel are not important, just find the strips and tops) 1⃣️It is impossible to shake the front and back. The blue graffiti in P2 and P3 are obviously long and tops, and the Dimoo letters on the front are the most obvious! You can feel it by putting your thumb on. Near the bottom is a symmetrical front and rear top box, you can feel it with a slight press. You can feel an accessory shaking the orange box in the upper left corner of P3. (It depends on the placement of the accessories, and the boxing points will be different) 2⃣️ Up and down, left and right can almost not shake, up and down because the baby is tall, left and right is because the accessories and desiccant are stuck on both sides. The accessories are on the picture surface, and the desiccant is on the barcode surface (small package of desiccant). You can only hear the sound of the desiccant shaking inside when you shake up and down. 3⃣️The bottom of P4 is placed with the baby face facing back. The strips on the front Dimoo are opposite to the top of the boat, and the two strips on the bottom are the chassis. Overall, it is a very clear box, which is very similar to the hidden one of Labubu Coca-Cola. Just look for strips and tops. Dimoo was shaking on the Willy, so cute! I wish you don’t miss it if you meet it. #Pop Mart #dimoo new product #DIMOO Disney joint brand #blind box feel sharing #blind box hide #blind box hide #hidden feel sharing #hide #Captain Willy #DIMOO Disney series hide
